---
title: exceed_max_rlp_block_size (EIP-7934)
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB

    [*] --> q_init
    q_init --> q_encode : encoded_size = len(rlp.encode(block))
    q_encode --> q_check : compare encoded_size to MAX_RLP_BLOCK_SIZE
    q_check --> q_reject : encoded_size > MAX_RLP_BLOCK_SIZE
    q_check --> q_accept : encoded_size <= MAX_RLP_BLOCK_SIZE
    q_reject --> q_final : return True
    q_accept --> q_final : return False
    q_final --> [*]

    note right of q_check
        INV-001: MAX_RLP_BLOCK_SIZE = MAX_BLOCK_SIZE - SAFETY_MARGIN = 8388608 bytes
        INV-002: Function is a pure predicate with no side effects
        INV-003: rlp.encode(block) is deterministic for a given block
    end note
